title: Alternate Reality
description:
Perfecting and polishing sounds for an audience of fans is the niche of each individual producer, but while there are some collaborations, most tracks will never see themselves beside each other unless taken by the hands of a dj and mixed indiscriminately, building a singular thought from multiple standalone titles released under different artists and labels. Alternate Reality combines seven different artists in the genres of Trance, DnB, House, and Dubstep to create an unprecedented journey into the universal consciousness; what these artists share whether they are aware of it or not. (This mix was originally titled 'Fresh Trax #3') Mixed By Ltjohnson on 11/23 2012

01 2808 - Nero
02 Crystallize - Lindsey Stirling
03 New Life - Nero
04 Calypso - Datsik & Excision
05 Pump it Up - Zomboy
06 Scary Monsters (Zed Mix) - Zed
07 Scary Monsters (Remix) - Noisia
08 Guilt - Nero
